#5511
@@yThe Desert Approach@@N~
A vast expanse of sun-bleached desert stretches to the horizon in every direction,
broken only by the tremendous shadow cast by the pyramid looming before you. The heat
is absolute, the silence broken only by the dry whisper of sand across stone.
~
