#5512
@@yThe Grand Entrance Plaza@@N~
Enormous carved pylons flank the approach to the pyramid, their faces still bearing
faint traces of paint that once blazed in red, blue, and gold. Colossal statues of
seated pharaohs observe the approach with expressions of serene and total authority.
~
