#5513
@@yThe Outer Vestibule@@N~
Two rows of granite columns support a low ceiling painted deep blue with gold
stars in constellations sacred to the cult of Ra. The air here is immediately cooler
than outside, carrying the dry mineral scent of cut stone that has never seen rain.
~
